Dimensions' End

Facing the Dimensions' End

In order to face the challenges in the Dimensions' End, it is necessary to meet the following requirements.

Dimensions' End: Order (5 tiers), Dimensions' End: Pathos (7 tiers)
• Three allies raised to at least level 60 and crystal strength 60

Dimensions' End: Entropy (20 tiers)
• All Dimensions' End: Order quests cleared to

Dimensions' End: Transcendence (periodically updated with new tiers)
• First five tiers of Dimensions' End: Entropy quests cleared to
Rewards in Dimensions' End

A general breakdown of the rewards available from the Dimensions' End is as follows.

Dimensions' End: Order
• EX Power Tokens (Dimensions' End: Order)
　Can be traded for applicable characters' 5★ EX weapons.

Dimensions' End: Pathos
• Draw Tickets
　A ticket that can be traded in for one draw.
• Ruin's Adamantine Nugget
　Can be refined into Ruin's adamantine ingots, used to perform a limit break on certain weapons.

Dimensions' End: Entropy
• Ruin's Adamantine Nugget
　Can be refined into Ruin's adamantine ingots, used to perform a limit break on certain weapons.
• Refuge's Adamantine Nugget
　Can be refined into Refuge's adamantine ingots, used to perform a limit break on certain armor.

Dimensions' End: Transcendence
• High Guard Token
　Can be traded for 7★ armor.
• Burst Power Token
　Can be traded for BT weapons.
Rank Plates
Rank plates of higher grades are awarded according to your progress in Dimensions' End: Entropy and Dimensions' End: Transcendence.
In Dimensions' End: Entropy, higher rank plates are awarded according to how many quests are simultaneously cleared to .
If all quests in Dimensions' End: Entropy are cleared to , your rank plate's grade will further increase according to how many reckoning quests are simultaneously cleared to in Dimensions' End: Transcendence.
Dimensions' End: Transcendence ranking conditions will change with the addition of new tiers, so your rank plate may change at that time as well.

E.g., an adamantine rank plate before new tiers are added may become diamond after the tiers have been added.

*Please refer to Dimensions' End: Transcendence notices for further details.
